eczema/irc 0.3


SET YOUR NICK, USERNAME AND "REAL NAME" 

  "GeckoExcrement" "geckoffee" "100% Certified Organic" IDENTITY!


CONNECT TO AN IRC SERVER EXPOSED VIA WEB SOCKET

  "ws://127.0.0.1:9000" CONNECT Socket !

  Take the websocket URI from your favourite IRC network's webchat,
  or spawn a websocket server (eg: websocketd + socat) that will
  forward a connection to your prefered IRC server instead.


INTERACTION

  + Raw Commands via SEND

    "PRIVMSG UptightUser :unsolicited message!" SEND


  + Dedicated Command Words 

    "#channel" /join
    "#channel" /who
    "nick" /whois
    "artisanally handcrafted spam!" "HipsterInASafariSuit" /msg

    See "commands.es" for more information.


  + No PING?

    Use KEEP-ALIVE if the server does not generate PING requests.


